item.title: 2004 Fleetwood Bounder 32w
item.description: FOR SALE Clean, well maintained, 2nd owner, everything in working condition. Never lived in full time and haven’t travelled with pets. Come take a look, you will not be disappointed. Accessories include: Onan 5500 generator 2 slides 2 A/C units HD TV leveling jacks backup camera banks power exhaust steering stabilizer tire pressure sensors solar (small) electric awning full size RV cover and tire covers Graphics faded and cracking.
